snippet: A 1922 Packard Twin Six is one of 16 original, unrestored entries scheduled to compete at the Pebble Beach Concours d’Élégance on Sunday in California.
abstract: Collector car world attending Pebble Beach Concours d’Elegance in California will have rare opportunity to view a 1922 Packard Twin Six, one of 16 original, unrestored entries that will be on display at the charity event.
lead_paragraph: A 1922 Packard Twin Six is one of 16 original, unrestored entries scheduled to compete at the Pebble Beach Concours d’Élégance on Sunday in California.
